content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.33 - Disabled, abandoned, or illegally parked vehicles subject to removal

State Regulations

The airport operator may remove from any area of the
airport any vehicle which is disabled, abandoned, parked in violation of these
rules and regulations, or which presents an operational problem, at the
operator's expense and without liability for damage which may result from such
removal. Notes
